org.gitlab.api

Class GitlabCommit.ProjectQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gitlab.api.GitlabCommit.ProjectQuery
  • Enclosing class:
    GitlabCommit

    public static class GitlabCommit.ProjectQuery
extends java.lang.Object
    This extends GitlabQuery and supports query for GitlabCommits within a GitlabProject with searching scope and range. Build this query with setters and call query() to execute query.

    Gitlab Web API: https://docs.gitlab.com/ee/api/commits.html#list-repository-commits

    GET /projects/:id/repository/commits
